title: Wet Dreams and Wet Dreams II - The Players
description:
'Wet Dreams'
Heavy Metal, 2000, 55 pages

'Wet Dreams II - The Players'
Heavy Metal, 2003, 55 pages

Four independent stories linked together by a necklace or key that gives access to the Sacred City.

Written and Illustrated by Alfonso Azpiri

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Honestly, I haven't read these. But Azpiri does some pretty stellar art (very European comic looking) in general and the other stuff I've read from him was always enjoyable. Looks like some kind of future tech, swords and guns, fantasy kind of stuff, with boobs (not porn style).
